OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774710680
OL,3,CArson arrest after house explosion
OL,5,FA man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,6,Fof arson with intent to endanger life
OL,7,Fafter a house explosion.
OL,9,FNeighbours say they heard "an almighty
OL,10,Fbang" in the usually quiet village of
OL,11,FHambleton, in Lancashire, just before
OL,12,F9.55am on 27 March, before discovering
OL,13,Fthe explosion and fire.
OL,15,FEmergency Services were called, and a
OL,16,F54-year-old man was taken to hospital
OL,17,Fwith minor injuries, North West
OL,18,FAmbulance Service said. No one else
OL,19,Fhad been injured.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
