OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774710680
OL,3,CArson arrest after house explosion
OL,5,FLancashire Police said an
OL,6,Finvestigation was now underway, but it
OL,7,Fwas being treated as an "isolated
OL,8,Fincident".
OL,10,FSome surrounding properties have been
OL,11,Fevacuated and Carr Lane remains
OL,12,Fclosed, the force added.
OL,14,FA large cordon was put in place, along
OL,15,Fwith a number of road closures, while
OL,16,Fengineers from both Electricity North
OL,17,FWest and Cadent, which manages the gas
OL,18,Fnetwork, were also called to the scene.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774710680
OL,3,CArson arrest after house explosion
OL,5,FCadent has since confirmed the
OL,6,Fexplosion is not directly linked to
OL,7,Fthe gas network staff are on scene to
OL,8,Fmake the area safe.
OL,10,FIn a statement, Lancashire Police
OL,11,Fsaid: "Shortly before 9:55am today, we
OL,12,Freceived a report from the fire
OL,13,Fservice of a fire at a property on
OL,14,FCarr Lane, Hambleton.
OL,16,F"Our officers along with other
OL,17,Femergency service colleagues are at
OL,18,Fthe scene and the fire service are
OL,19,Fworking to extinguish the fire.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774710680
OL,3,CArson arrest after house explosion
OL,5,F"A 54-year-old man has been arrested
OL,6,Fon suspicion of Arson with intent to
OL,7,Fendanger life. He has been taken to
OL,8,Fhospital with minor injuries at this
OL,9,Ftime.
OL,11,F"Thankfully, no one else has been
OL,12,Finjured.
OL,14,F"A small number of surrounding
OL,15,Fproperties have been evacuated and
OL,16,FCarr Lane remains closed whilst our
OL,17,Fcolleagues carry out work to ensure
OL,18,Fthe safety of the area.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774710680
OL,3,CArson arrest after house explosion
OL,5,F"An investigation is underway, and a
OL,6,Fman has been arrested. This is being
OL,7,Ftreated as an isolated incident.
OL,9,F"Anyone with information is asked to
OL,10,Fcall 101 quoting log 0289 of 27th
OL,11,FMarch."
OL,13,FNorth West Ambulance Service added:
OL,14,F"We attended the scene with
OL,15,Fsignificant resources, including
OL,16,Fadvanced clinicians, operational
OL,17,Fcommanders, air ambulance and the
OL,18,FHazardous Area Response Team.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774710680
OL,3,CArson arrest after house explosion
OL,5,F"One patient was taken to the hospital
OL,6,Ffor further assessment with minor
OL,7,Finjuries."
OL,9,FLancashire Fire and Rescue Service
OL,10,Fsaid: "Lancashire Fire and Rescue
OL,11,FService were called at 09:51 this
OL,12,Fmorning (27th March) to reports of an
OL,13,Fexplosion and fire at a domestic
OL,14,Fproperty on Carr Lane in Hambleton.
OL,16,F"Fire engines from Preesall, Bispham,
OL,17,FFleetwood and South Shore attended,
OL,18,Falong with an aerial ladder platform
OL,19,Ffrom Blackpool. Crews used two hose
OL,20,Freels and two sets of breathing
OL,21,Fapparatus to tackle the fire.
OL,26,@oD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774710680
OL,3,CArson arrest after house explosion
OL,5,F"The incident is now under control,
OL,6,Fand the number of fire engines in
OL,7,Fattendance has been reduced to one. A
OL,8,Fjoint investigation with the police is
OL,9,Fcurrently underway to establish the
OL,10,Fcause of the explosion."
OL,12,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,13,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,14,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,15,Four region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
